HEADWORD: Aha
<hw>A*ha"</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>interj.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Ah</ets>,
interj. + <ets>ha</ets>.]</ety> <def>An exclamation expressing, by
different intonations, triumph, mixed with derision or irony, or simple
surprise.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Aha</ent>⟦br⟧

